    <div class="fancliq__about__body">
        <div class="fancliq__about__header">
            About Fancliq
        </div>
        <p class="fancliq__about__item">
            Fancliq is image centric social media for youth sports that is built on a "gig economy" model for photographers.
        </p>
        <p class="fancliq__about__item">
            Fancliq's creates an income opportunity for photographers in the same way that Uber and AirBnB create income opportunities. Turn your home, car or camera into income.
        </p>
        <p class="fancliq__about__item">
            We pay photographers to shoot youth sports on a per game basis. The photographers determine what event, "where" and "when" to shoot. Fancliq photographers are free to shoot as often as they want. Our photographers don't have to own a studio, market, edit, sell or deliver the images. They get to do what they love, shoot pictures and get paid for doing so.
        </p>
        <p class="fancliq__about__item">
            Fancliq does all the drudgery work to process the images and deliver them as beautiful photographs to the parent's mobile phone.
        </p>
